====英格兰与俄罗斯球迷冲突====
开赛前一天，马赛当地街头混混与英格兰球迷爆发冲突。警方利用催泪弹驱散人群，逮捕了一名当地混混和一名英格兰球迷<ref>{{cite news|title=Euro 2016: England fan arrested after Marseille clash|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-36496745|accessdate=2016-06-10|publisher=BBC Sport|date=2016-06-10|archive-date=2016-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160610081319/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-36496745|dead-url=no}}</ref>。6月11日英格兰对阵俄罗斯1-1平局的比赛当天，比赛前后当地再度发生街头暴力冲突<ref name="BBC">{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/uk-36506917|title=Euro 2016: Violence mars England-Russia match - BBC News|website=BBC News|language=en-GB|access-date=2016-06-11|archive-date=2019-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190714020132/https://www.bbc.com/news/uk-36506917|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一名英格兰球迷据报因伤情严重送院医治，另有数十人受伤<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2016/06/11/england-and-russia-fans-clash-in-marseilles-ahead-of-euro-2016-g/|title=England fan fighting for his life  and dozens more injured as English fans and Russian thugs clash at Euro 2016 in Marseille|website=The Telegraph|access-date=2016-06-11|archive-date=2016-06-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160611184604/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/2016/06/11/england-and-russia-fans-clash-in-marseilles-ahead-of-euro-2016-g/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。次日，欧洲足联开始针对比赛上种族主义行为和燃放信号弹等“难以接受”的场面，向[[俄罗斯足球总会|俄罗斯足球总会]]展开纪律调查程序<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-36510550 |title=Euro 2016: 'Disgusted' Uefa charge Russia over fan violence |publisher=BBC News |date=2016-06-12 |accessdate=2016-06-12 |archive-date=2016-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160612101231/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-europe-36510550 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。6月14日，欧足联开出罚单，俄足协被处以15万欧元的罚款以及“缓期逐出欧锦赛”（[[缓刑|缓刑]]）的处罚<ref>{{cite web |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2016-06/15/c_129062210.htm |title=球迷再闹就出局 俄罗斯队受到欧锦赛出局“缓刑”处罚 |publisher=新华社 |date=2016-06-15 |accessdate=2016-06-15 |archive-date=2016-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160815194818/http://news.xinhuanet.com/world/2016-06/15/c_129062210.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並发布声明，称若再次爆发暴力行为应取消两支球队的参赛资格<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-36510550 |title=Euro 2016: England and Russia given disqualification warning |publisher=BBC News |date=2016-06-12 |accessdate=2016-06-12 |archive-date=2016-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160612110250/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-europe-36510550 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

====尼斯球迷冲突====
6月11日，北爱尔兰对波兰赛事前夕，双方球迷遭当地人及法国球迷袭击，多人受伤。冲突发生的地点在尼斯著名的海滨大道上，大量北爱尔兰队及波兰队球迷来到这里，等待两队之间的比赛。其时，在马塞纳广场附近，一伙尼斯当地青年试图挑起两队球迷间的矛盾，但两队球迷并没有发生冲突，而是共同将矛头指向这伙当地青年。场面一度陷入混乱，最终出动了防暴警察才将冲突平息下来。

次日凌晨2点，一位来自北爱尔兰巴利米纳市的球迷名从法国尼斯市的一处海滨大道上坠亡，年仅25岁。不过，这名球迷的死亡是否与比赛之前尼斯市发生的球迷冲突事件有直接关系，还有待进一步调查<ref>{{cite web |url=http://sports.sina.com.cn/g/euro/2016-06-13/doc-ifxszkzy5208142.shtml |title=欧洲杯出人命了!一球迷坠亡 或与暴力冲突有关 |publisher=新浪体育讯 |date=2016-06-13 |accessdate=2016-06-13 |archive-date=2016-06-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160616091147/http://sports.sina.com.cn/g/euro/2016-06-13/doc-ifxszkzy5208142.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

====里耳球迷衝突====
6月12日，[[烏克蘭國家足球隊|烏克蘭]]對[[德國國家足球隊|德國]]賽事前夕，雙方球迷於[[里耳|里耳]]街頭衝突，最少造成兩人受傷<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.tvb.com/world/575ddc066db28c075f000001/ |title=歐洲足協警告球迷若再滋事 英俄或被取消資格 |accessdate=2016-06-14 |archive-date=2016-08-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160808182557/http://news.tvb.com/world/575ddc066db28c075f000001/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

====球迷扔煙火====
6月17日，在[[聖伊天|聖伊天]][[若弗鲁瓦·吉夏尔球场|若弗鲁瓦·吉夏尔球场]]舉行的D組第二-{zh-hans:轮;zh-hant:輪;}-賽事，由{{nft|捷克}}迎戰{{nft|克羅地亞}}。在賽事尾段，多名克羅地亞球迷向場內投擲多枚燃點了的煙花。其中一枚更在場內爆炸，比賽一度需要暫停。多名克羅地亞球迷又在看台上打架。歐洲足協宣布，對克羅地亞足總展開紀律程序。在同日進行的D組第二-{zh-hans:轮;zh-hant:輪;}-賽事{{nft|西班牙}}對{{nft|土耳其}}，土耳其球迷衝入球場，以及賽後在場內燃點煙花，土耳其足總同樣面臨紀律聆訊。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=182972 |title=克羅地亞土耳其面臨歐洲足協紀律聆訊 |accessdate=2016-06-19 |archive-date=2016-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160829035738/http://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=182972 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

兩宗事件再次引起球迷討論場内保安問題，再加上去年11月經歷過[[2015年11月巴黎袭击事件|巴黎恐襲]]，不少質疑法國經歷過恐襲爲何易燃物品仍然會順利通過安檢進入球場。

===场地品质===
法国足球场因品质差在小组赛期间受到批评。法国教练[[迪迪埃·德尚|迪迪埃·德尚]]的批评尤为严重<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fourfourtwo.com/news/deschamps-blasts-velodrome-pitch|title=Deschamps blasts Velodrome pitch|publisher=FourFourTwo|date=2016-06-15|accessdate=2016-06-29|archive-date=2016-06-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160630141526/http://www.fourfourtwo.com/news/deschamps-blasts-velodrome-pitch|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.espnfc.co.uk/european-championship/story/2894743/france-manager-didier-deschamps-blames-ac-dc-concert-for-poor-pitch-conditions|title=France manager Didier Deschamps blames AC/DC concert for poor pitch|publisher=ESPN FC|first1=Mark|last1=Rodden|first2=Dan|last2=Kilpatrick|date=2016-06-16|accessdate=2016-06-29|archive-date=2016-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160704083538/http://www.espnfc.co.uk/european-championship/story/2894743/france-manager-didier-deschamps-blames-ac-dc-concert-for-poor-pitch-conditions|dead-url=no}}</ref>。欧足联赛事总监马丁·凯伦（{{lang|en|Martin Kallen}}）指责暴雨损坏草皮，但媒体推测非足球活动也可能是因素之一<ref>{{cite news |last=Dunbar |first=Graham |date=2016-06-17 |title=UEFA blames heavy rain for damaging fields at Euro 2016 |url=http://bigstory.ap.org/article/d943730e49ed4f759c2600795c4bc6e8/uefa-blames-heavy-rain-damaging-fields-euro-2016 |agency=Associated Press |accessdate=2016-06-19 |archive-date=2016-06-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160618155742/http://www.bigstory.ap.org/article/d943730e49ed4f759c2600795c4bc6e8/uefa-blames-heavy-rain-damaging-fields-euro-2016 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.skysports.com/football/news/19692/10316717/euro-2016-pitches-should-be-better-says-uefa-official|title=Euro 2016 pitches 'should be better' says UEFA official|publisher=Sky Sports|date=2016-06-17|accessdate=2016-06-29|archive-date=2016-06-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160620204203/http://www.skysports.com/football/news/19692/10316717/euro-2016-pitches-should-be-better-says-uefa-official|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

里尔的球场因球员不断打滑受到特别的关注，半场结束时场地管理人员被迫尝试修复裂开的草坪<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rte.ie/sport/euro-2016/2016/0621/797182-uefa-to-replace-lille-pitch-after-ireland-game/|title=UEFA to replace Lille pitch after Ireland clash|publisher=|accessdate=2016-07-04|archive-date=2016-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160623124352/http://www.rte.ie/sport/euro-2016/2016/0621/797182-uefa-to-replace-lille-pitch-after-ireland-game/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。尽管欧足联采用多种方法纠正存在的问题，比如禁止比赛前在草坪上训练、施肥、播种、割草、[[光照治疗|光照治疗]]、干燥并在比赛时关闭顶篷以避免雨淋，但里尔的草坪还是必须在6月22日意大利对阵意大利的小组赛结束后全数更换<ref>{{cite web|url=http://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-soccer-euro-pitch-lille-idUKKCN0Z726M|title=UEFA decides to replace Lille pitch after poor weather|publisher=|accessdate=2016-07-04|archive-date=2016-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160817181108/http://uk.reuters.com/article/uk-soccer-euro-pitch-lille-idUKKCN0Z726M|dead-url=no}}</ref>。新草坪被换上荷兰草，为6月26日德国对阵斯洛伐克的十六强赛作准备<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rte.ie/sport/euro-2016/2016/0624/798003-lille-groundsmen-place-their-faith-in-dutch-grass/|title=Lille groundsmen place their faith in Dutch grass|publisher=|accessdate=2016-07-04|archive-date=2016-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160627141241/http://www.rte.ie/sport/euro-2016/2016/0624/798003-lille-groundsmen-place-their-faith-in-dutch-grass/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://indianexpress.com/article/sports/football/euro-2016-new-pitch-in-lille-already-familiar-to-germany-2872012/ |title=Euro 2016: New pitch in Lille already familiar to Germany |accessdate=2016-07-07 |archive-date=2016-06-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160628103334/http://indianexpress.com/article/sports/football/euro-2016-new-pitch-in-lille-already-familiar-to-germany-2872012/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.irishmirror.ie/sport/soccer/soccer-news/pitch-lille-euro-2016-venue-8270082|title=Pitch at Lille Euro 2016 venue replaced ahead of Germany vs Slovakia last-16 tie|first=James|last=Whaling|date=2016-06-23|publisher=|accessdate=2016-07-04|archive-date=2016-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160919220717/http://www.irishmirror.ie/sport/soccer/soccer-news/pitch-lille-euro-2016-venue-8270082|dead-url=no}}</ref>。欧足联还表示，圣但尼和马赛的球场也需要修复<ref name="uefa-replacepitch">{{cite web|url=http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuro/news/newsid=2381790.html?rss=2381790%20Stade%20Pierre-Mauroy%20pitch%20to%20be%20replaced|title=Stade Pierre Mauroy pitch to be replaced - UEFA EURO - News - UEFA.com|first=|last=UEFA.com|publisher=|accessdate=2016-07-04|archive-date=2016-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161109070255/http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuro/news/newsid=2381790.html?rss=2381790%20Stade%20Pierre-Mauroy%20pitch%20to%20be%20replaced|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

欧足联的利兹顾问理查德·海登（Richard Hayden）曾下令里尔、尼斯和马赛三弟球场管理者将球场换上由一家奥地利公司提供的估价60万英镑（约合46万欧元）的斯洛伐克草坪而遭到批评。据报道，6月22日，法国草坪协会官员因屡次出现的草坪问题指责海登，指出“今天只有这些草坪有问题是非常惊人的<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/football/2016/06/22/euro-2016-turf-war-french-blames-english-based-groundsman-over-p/|title=Euro 2016 turf war: French blame English-based groundsman over 'poor pitches'|newspaper=The Daily Telegraph|first=Tom|last=Morgan|date=2016-06-22|accessdate=2016-06-29|archive-date=2016-06-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160628004245/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/football/2016/06/22/euro-2016-turf-war-french-blames-english-based-groundsman-over-p/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”欧足联发表声明驳斥称对海登的批评是毫无根据的，并表示他们对他的工作表示满意<ref name="uefa-replacepitch"/>。

==市场推广==
===会徽和口号===
2013年6月26日，官方标志在巴黎帕维荣坎邦宴会厅（{{lang|fr|Pavillon Cambon Capucines}}）揭晓<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.uefa.com/MultimediaFiles/Download/EuroExperience/competitions/EURO/01/96/71/90/1967190_DOWNLOAD.pdf|title=UEFA EURO 2016 logo Launch|date=2013-06-26|work=UEFA.com|accessdate=2013-06-28|archive-date=2013-08-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130817082244/http://www.uefa.com/MultimediaFiles/Download/EuroExperience/competitions/EURO/01/96/71/90/1967190_DOWNLOAD.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref> 。标志由葡萄牙事务所布兰蒂亚中心（{{lang|en|Brandia Centralz}}），沿用了以前的欧洲杯视觉标识，其设计基于“庆祝足球艺术”的主题。标志描绘了亨利·德劳内杯（{{lang|en|Henri Delaunay}}），配以法国国旗蓝、白、红三色，被代表着各种艺术运动和足球元素的形状和线条的混合体包围<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuro/finals/news/newsid=1966170.html|title=UEFA EURO 2016 logo unveiled|date=2013-06-26|work=UEFA.com|accessdate=2013-06-28|archive-date=2013-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130627052118/http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuro/finals/news/newsid=1966170.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2013年10月17日，欧足联公布赛事官方口号“普天同庆”（{{lang|fr|Le Rendez-Vous}}）。问及其含义时，2016年欧锦赛组委会主席雅克·兰伯特（{{lang|fr|Jacques Lambert}}）表示，口号“比比赛日期和场地更能提醒人”。他进一步解释称“欧足联正向全世界球迷和主要赛事爱好者发出邀请函，邀请他们见面，共享精英级赛事的气氛<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuro/finals/news/newsid=2010153.html|title=UEFA EURO 2016: 'Le Rendez-Vous'|publisher=UEFA.com|date=2013-10-17|accessdate=2016-05-28|archive-date=2015-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151114205347/http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuro/finals/news/newsid=2010153.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

===电子游戏===
